{"tid":295690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Bitcoin  /  Ethereum 雲端掘礦教學","createTime":"2017-06-24T03:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T04:38:25.000Z","uid":124637,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa2018920aa63d0a1aa0d952fcbf1242d57c659","tid":295690,"uid":124637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"最近開始玩 Bitcoin  /  Ethereum 大升，見連登都出左好多教學，以太坊挖矿<br />\n但見到多數都係直接買 或者 水龍頭，如果唔想直接買，自已掘得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\n而家要自己掘有兩種方法，一種係自已機掘，可以用MinerGate，<br />\n另一種係俾錢叫人幫你掘， 就好似Genesis mining。以下會慢慢解釋下。<br />\n<br />\n家陣靠自己機去掘大路野(Bitcoin, ETH)，真係好難，可以講掘黎哂電費（公司機除外），<br />\n大多數都係靠掘唔出名貨幣，去換返 Bitcoin／ ETH。<br />\n<br />\nMinerGate 傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://minergate.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fminergate.com%2F&d=V%2FzvkibrovXKhrUX6s6g7y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b2fece74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://minergate.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/110936_0b47adabb241221ffbcbdda46cb9f114.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F24%2F110936_0b47adabb241221ffbcbdda46cb9f114.png&h=3e69f03e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去當然係按&rdquo; Download Miner &amp; Start Mining&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n申請一個ACC，裝完登入，就可以開波。<br />\n入到程式，你可以乜都唔理，就咁按中間綠色制開始掘。<br />\n佢會自動幫你掘上一個鐘最高exchange rate 貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/111351_18ea22d3a9b45f88c29000c9f6573c52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F24%2F111351_18ea22d3a9b45f88c29000c9f6573c52.png&h=3512dcdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔鐘意，可以自已選掘D 乜貨幣又得，又可以SET 用幾多資源去掘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/111527_d00527740b8eaf91ae3b674e689471ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F24%2F111527_d00527740b8eaf91ae3b674e689471ab.png&h=d1586a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一種係俾錢叫人幫你掘，Genesis mining 就係其中一 款。<br />\n<br />\nGenesis mining 傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.genesis-mining.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.genesis-mining.com%2F&d=V%2FzvkibrovXKhrUX6s6g7y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=db59b9dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.genesis-mining.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n佢原理就好簡單，就係你俾錢，佢幫你掘，掘完俾返你。<br />\n<br />\n當然又係要申請ACC登入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/111954_49577b299da21e4dc43bc9db6feb4331.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F24%2F111954_49577b299da21e4dc43bc9db6feb4331.png&h=f686a191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後有興趣玩，就可以買佢D plan, 暫時得 bitcoin, ETH, XMR 三種。<br />\n收費會有D唔同，要睇清楚。<br />\n暫時係 ETH ( 以太坊挖矿) 最底玩，因為BITCOIN 要收 維護費。<br />\n<br />\n買完，佢夠一定數量就會入落你戶口。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔介意，可以用我推廣碼g7WKBi 買plan，會有3 % discount。"},{"pid":"0b21cbc939360e7bbd678389fd2a1def671e5d28","tid":295690,"uid":76117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afcd21ed4df958770ce28564835064283fc6faeb","tid":295690,"uid":76117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:45:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa82822408644bb05821260f3903406752281120","tid":295690,"uid":124637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"成本唔高， 掘下d未升ge , 可能爆出唔定， 最多輸電費。"},{"pid":"dd430f85e25c43457d98a37b7b2ec894ba76e97b","tid":295690,"uid":124637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T06:49:13.000Z","msg":"無人有玩？"},{"pid":"c4d213bd38e3362115f8755d2cddec32242fc212","tid":295690,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T07:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人有玩？</blockquote><br />\n你開架個網？"},{"pid":"91787866fd1bb0b1f8ea4b044f1cd1c05a991b01","tid":295690,"uid":117556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T07:18:47.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"e66bb06802435c00a537de9a36d8da5e7e045ecb","tid":295690,"uid":124637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無人有玩？</blockquote><br />\n你開架個網？</blockquote><br />\n我都想<br />\n寫post睇下有無bro有更好推介"},{"pid":"8bc368d925bb6fbb231d631e0c49adc7b55914f8","tid":295690,"uid":12888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:02:12.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a8f476eea465fb25cce9a133f5acb861116c94","tid":295690,"uid":6706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"好多時都係scam，你有冇了解清楚先推薦俾大家<br />\n個genesis我見啲鬼佬係昆水"},{"pid":"4ade32b194faa1127a8918bfb72d825b66527aee","tid":295690,"uid":6706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多時都係scam，你有冇了解清楚先推薦俾大家<br />\n個genesis我見啲鬼佬話係昆水</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2df1bbbffdcd1560e6998831ab74085042ea06ca","tid":295690,"uid":9265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T06:02:08.000Z","msg":"搵隻it狗幫你砌都得啦 咁簡單又可以隨時放曬套野"},{"pid":"5bdd1704e1eeb938ad59ad63b1b713eb7cfb7d8e","tid":295690,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"矿你老母"},{"pid":"f76409eb4910a5d85ad5310a89f8823ce74e74ea","tid":295690,"uid":124637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T23:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多時都係scam，你有冇了解清楚先推薦俾大家<br />\n個genesis我見啲鬼佬係昆水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自已緊係有用喇， minergate用處就係方便， 唔洗搞甘多野，mac都用到。<br />\n但有人話過會用左你資源幫佢自已掘，<br />\n同轉返出黎要收手續費。<br />\n其實呢層好正常， 人地做個程式出黎， 都要賺下錢。<br />\n<br />\ngenesis  miner就我見好多bro都有買。<br />\n同夠數可以即時攞出黎，都算底玩。<br />\n當然投資一定有風險， 自已考慮。"},{"pid":"73bea6d37d135bd948270fea04576000843ee9ae","tid":295690,"uid":124637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T23:36:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵隻it狗幫你砌都得啦 咁簡單又可以隨時放曬套野</blockquote><br />\n聽d bro講佛山租地方搞tim"},{"pid":"856a494cd1b727645d1d980dc663d8ea9ad7c8c4","tid":295690,"uid":124637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"有D水龍頭網，話只要開住就有bitcoin 收，其實有真有假，就算有，都唔會太多錢。 <br />\n所以我想講下我用過ge 水龍頭網分享下。 <br />\n<br />\n1. StartMiner <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/104728_8ee09f3e8e764b043b17362383da44d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F104728_8ee09f3e8e764b043b17362383da44d4.png&h=9a7b3df2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個水龍頭網話開住等就有錢。 <br />\n夠0.005 就可以攞出黎，仲話可以買plan 加快速度。 <br />\n又話可以睇到佢之前呢個網攞出黎ge 錢。 <br />\n<br />\n但去到0.005, 佢就會自已restet, 根本無可能攞到，完全呃人，大家要小心。"},{"pid":"e7b27606f1fce194293088cbfaead4ab33c5fe38","tid":295690,"uid":125621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T19:41:22.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6027eaf6a75e677b73a7511426e76cee5d3d78ea","tid":295690,"uid":14054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T16:49:42.000Z","msg":"其實原理係咩？<br />\n點解叫掘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2fa4c5137037e9b222dbff1af340bbfc85123fe","tid":295690,"uid":124637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實原理係咩？<br />\n點解叫掘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你問雲端定自已掘先？"},{"pid":"df2ad6a009ca6d3c8a67b0e2730faa27d4d2f4f6","tid":295690,"uid":127727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T23:33:14.000Z","msg":"minergate唔好再用啦 <br />\n呢幾個月食左好多錢<br />\n一值有唔見錢既情況"},{"pid":"ee2648953b2a4e76cf753a744af894122eab170b","tid":295690,"uid":35574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>minergate唔好再用啦 <br />\n呢幾個月食左好多錢<br />\n一值有唔見錢既情況</blockquote><br />\n本身挖左1日係有coin 第3日開黎睇全部0晒"},{"pid":"105e6a2a8e2d0a24b0c84ce05b05fb4f0024f55d","tid":295690,"uid":127727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:38:25.000Z","msg":"個幾月前巳經開始食錢"}]}